Rice Krispy Treat Recipe
https://modernmealmakeover.com/rice-krispie-treats-recipe/
April King

6 Tbsp unsalted butter
1/2 cup sweetened condensed milk
1 tsp vanilla extract
16 oz mini marshmallows
6 cups rice krispy cereal

Lightly grease a 9Ã—13 baking dish.

In a large pot, melt butter until bubbly.  Add sweetened condensed milk and
stir until it comes to a boil. Continue cooking for one minute.  Add vanilla
and marshmallows, and stir until marshmallows are completely melted.

Remove from heat and add rice krispy cereal. Stir to mix well coating all the
rice cereal.

Pour into a lightly greased baking dish and press GENTLY with your fingers to
spread.

Allow rice krispies to set for 30-45 minutes before cutting into and serving.
Enjoy!
